Index entries for signature-permutations of Catalan automorphisms
xref: Inverse: A125988. a(n) = A125985(A125985(n)). The number of cycles, fixed points, maximum cycle sizes and LCM's of all cycle sizes in range [A014137(n-1)..A014138(n-1)] of this permutation are given by A126294, A126295, A126296 and A126297. The fixed points are given by A126298/A126299.
